text: Birobidzhan (; Yiddish: ביראָבידזשאַן) is a town in Russia. It is the administrative center of the Jewish Autonomous Oblast, located on the Trans- Siberian railway, it is close to the Chinese border. As of 2019, 73,129 people lived there. ==Other websites== * Official website of Birobidzhan Category:Jewish Autonomous Oblast Category:Capitals of oblasts of Russia
